headline: Amcor to report fiscal 2025 second quarter and half year results
summary: Amcor plc (NYSE: AMCR; ASX: AMC) will announce its fiscal 2025 second quarter and half year results for the three and six month period ended 31 December 2024 respectively, before the US market opens on Tuesday 4 February 2025.
